snippet.title: SHINONOME PV
snippet.description:
Early access starts November 11, 17:00 on Steam!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1977910/_/
Using noises as clues, escape from a haunted house that changes appearance every time it’s entered
SHINONOME is a new type of escape game that tests your courage and quick wits
